cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper proposes an extension to GANs for generating artwork, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of back-propagation and label information also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The generation of complex and abstract images may also relate to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
